OL,3,CBristol Airport takes legal action
OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff investment
OL,6,F"The Welsh Government will defend this
OL,7,Flegal challenge. Cardiff Airport is of
OL,8,Fvital importance to the economy of the
OL,9,FSouth Wales region, with thousands of
OL,10,Fjobs stemming from the airport."
OL,12,FThe Competition Appeal Tribunal (CAT)
OL,13,Fis a specialist UK judicial body that
OL,14,Fhears and decides cases involved
OL,15,Fcompetition and economic regulatory
OL,16,Fissues.
