OL,3,CBristol Airport takes legal action
OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff investment
OL,6,FIn an open letter published in April
OL,7,Fthis year, Bristol Airport said: "No
OL,8,Fother airport in the UK has ever
OL,9,Freceived anything close to this level
OL,10,Fof public subsidy and as such it is
OL,11,Funprecedented and comes on top of the
OL,12,Fnearly #200m of taxpayers' money
OL,13,Falready provided to Cardiff Airport.
OL,15,F"Bristol Airport welcomes competition,
OL,16,Fbut this must be on a level playing
OL,17,Ffield to avoid market distortions.
