OL,3,CBristol Airport takes legal action
OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff investment
OL,6,F"This subsidy could move activity
OL,7,Fbetween locations at huge cost to the
OL,8,Ftaxpayer but without any net economic
OL,9,Fbenefit."
OL,11,FSpeaking at a plenary in the Senedd
OL,12,Ftoday, Rebecca Evans said: "We
OL,13,Fabsolutely recognise the importance of
OL,14,FCardiff Airport to the economy of the
OL,15,Fsouth Wales region, with thousands of
OL,16,Fjobs stemming from the airport and the
OL,17,Feconomic ecosystem that is supported
OL,18,Fby it.
