OL,3,CBristol Airport takes legal action
OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff investment
OL,6,F"We believe very strongly that with
OL,7,Fthe right investment, the airport has
OL,8,Fthe potential to make an even greater
OL,9,Fcontribution to the economy, creating
OL,10,Fadditional jobs and further boosting
OL,11,Fregional gross value added.
OL,13,F"The Welsh Government investment that
OL,14,Fwe propose will allow Welsh Ministers
OL,15,Fto oversee the strategic direction of
OL,16,Fthe airport on the delivery of long-
OL,17,Fterm economic growth, with a view to
OL,18,Frealising these benefits for the whole
OL,19,Fof the south Wales economy.
