OL,3,CBristol Airport takes legal action
OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff investment
OL,6,F"We've chosen to invest in the airport
OL,7,Fto ensure economic stability and
OL,8,Fgrowth around that whole region. I
OL,9,Fthink that our willingness to commit
OL,10,Fsignificant funding for the long term
OL,11,Fdoes reflect the confidence that we do
OL,12,Fhave in the airport's economic growth
OL,13,Fpotential.
OL,15,F"And, of course, just a reminder for
OL,16,Fcolleagues that the Welsh Government
OL,17,Fdoesn't run the airport, although
OL,18,FWales does own the airport."
