OL,3,CBristol Airport takes legal action
OL,4,Cover #205m Cardiff investment
OL,6,F"Labour has shown time and time again
OL,7,Fthat Ministers in Cardiff Bay have no
OL,8,Fidea how to run an airport and they
OL,9,Fshould follow calls from the Welsh
OL,10,FConservatives that this failing
OL,11,Fairport should be sold to the private
OL,12,Fsector, so that it can not only
OL,13,Fsurvive but thrive."
OL,15,FIt is not clear yet, how long legal
OL,16,Fproceedings will take before a
OL,17,Fconclusion is made. There will be no
OL,18,Fimpact on the day-to-day operations at
OL,19,FCardiff Airport.
